Warning


Warning about companies identifying themselves as companies of the Mizuho Financial Group.
Companies calling themselves "Mizuho Mergers & Acquisitions" , "Mizuho Investments Inc" and "Mizuho Investments Beverly Hills" have established websites and are engaged in activities on the Internet, identifying themselves as companies of the Mizuho Financial Group.  Please beware that those companies have absolutely no relationship or association with Mizuho Financial Group.














