Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 6:02 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd. engages in custody and administration, pension trust, and asset management businesses in Japan. The company offers custody and administration services related to asset management for money trusts, pecuniary trusts, investment trusts, securities trusts, and other types of trusts, as well as master trust services. It also provides services and product packages for corporate pension schemes, which include corporate pension plan design, management of pension policyholders and recipients, and asset management and custody, as well as investment solutions and review of pension schemes; introduction and management of defined contribution pension schemes; and disposit...
Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd. engages in custody and administration, pension trust, and asset management businesses in Japan. The company offers custody and administration services related to asset management for money trusts, pecuniary trusts, investment trusts, securities trusts, and other types of trusts, as well as master trust services. It also provides services and product packages for corporate pension schemes, which include corporate pension plan design, management of pension policyholders and recipients, and asset management and custody, as well as investment solutions and review of pension schemes; introduction and management of defined contribution pension schemes; and disposition-type employee stock ownership plans, retirement benefits, and compensation plans for senior executives. In addition, the company offers asset management products using various investment targets and methods, including hedge funds, privately laced real estate investment funds, concentrated investment funds, and package products; and equity and fixed income products, alternatives, and packaged funds. It operates through a network of 36 branches and 19 sub-branches. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan. Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Mizuho Financial Group, Inc.
Detailed Description


